thread.title: PayPal: Show Me the Venmo Money

author: Aaron Back
title: PayPal: Show Me the Venmo Money
text:
PayPal investors are getting a reminder that valuation still matters.
The payment company’s shares were trading down more than 6% Thursday morning after eBay said it would replace PayPal with an Amsterdam-based startup as its primary payments processor.
At first glance, this sharp reaction is puzzling. Following PayPal’s spinoff from eBay...
